 "remarks": "Charming and wellmaintained colonial offering 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and one half bath in a convenient Norwalk cul-de-sac location. The main level features a bright living room with a woodburning fireplace, a comfortable family room, and an inviting kitchen and dining area that make everyday living easy.  A finished lower level provides excellent bonus space for a playroom, home office, or media room. The home also includes a onecar garage for parking and storage.  One of the standout features of this property is its beautifully landscaped yard - a lush, wellcaredfor outdoor space perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Even better, lawn maintenance is included, giving you the benefit of a gorgeous yard without the lawn upkeep.  Movein ready with multiple living areas, classic colonial charm, and premium outdoor appeal.",
